  <brief_title>Conventional or Video-Assisted Surgery in Treating Patients With Lung Metastases</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase III Randomized Prospective Trial of Open Versus Minimally Invasive, Video-Assisted Resection of Pulmonary Metastases</official_title>
